description:
Web controls for easy forms development with validation support.

Example usage:
<ky:FieldSet ID="fs2" runat="server">
  <ky:FieldSetRow Label="Your Name" CssClass="ctrl">
    <ky:FieldSetItem Name="Name" Required="true"  />
  </ky:FieldSetRow>
  <ky:FieldSetRow Label="E-mail Adress" CssClass="ctrl">
    <ky:FieldSetItem Name="Email" Required="true" RegexName="Email" />
  </ky:FieldSetRow>
</ky:FieldSet>
